data.value:
This is to inform you that there is a new improved system version for the system.
Please download the latest version of the system.
Instructions: 1. Click download newest version or visit SDO Antique Official Website. 2. Locate the downloaded zip file (It is usually appear in your Downloads folder) and extract to drive C: and replace the file. 3. After extracted find and install crystal report(CR13SP31MSI32_0-10010309), if you've not yet installed crystal report. 3. Locate the Project Soldier application, right click and send it to Desktop. 4. For clarification and other inquiries, please contact: Email: ictservicessdoantique@deped.gov.ph Facebook Messenger: DepEd Antique ICT Contact Number: 09100716949
